aott/analysis/dataflow/constant_propagation.runa
Constant Propagation Analysis Module for AOTT Optimization

This module provides constant propagation analysis for the Runa AOTT system including:
- Compile-time constant evaluation
- Constant folding and algebraic simplification
- Conditional constant propagation
- Interprocedural constant analysis
- Lattice-based value tracking
- Sparse conditional constant propagation
- Range-based constant analysis
- Symbolic constant propagation
- Array constant tracking
- Structure constant analysis
- Constant expression recognition
- Branch elimination via constants
- Loop unrolling with constants
- Constant pool optimization
- Cross-tier constant sharing
:End Note

Import "dev/debug/errors/core" as Errors

